Subject: https://diviloper.dev/ontology#Contains_Headers_Param
Object: Specifies whether the input file contains headers. Defaults to True

Subject: https://diviloper.dev/ontology#Field_Delimiter

Subject: https://diviloper.dev/ontology#Import_CSV
Object: Import a CSV file from a url into a TabularDataset

Subject: https://diviloper.dev/ontology#Line_Dilimiter_Param
Object: Specifies the characters to use as line delimiters

Subject: https://diviloper.dev/ontology#Store_as_CSV
Object: Stores a TabularDataset as a CSV file

Subject: https://diviloper.dev/ontology#URL_Param

Object:
Method to use when aggregating a TabularDataset.
Should have the same dimensionality as the corresponding "aggregates" Parameter.
